data.description: Incredibly spacious, like new, move in ready home! You will be impressed when you walk into this amazing home with the open concept floor plan which provides a bright open space that is perfect for when family and friends gather together. 4 bedrooms, all with large walk in closets and 3 full baths. The 4th bedroom has an ensuite. You will appreciate the perfectly appointed expansive kitchen with center island. The master bedroom includes a sizable master bath with dual vanities and enormous tile shower. Outside you will find a convenient circular drive, covered front porch and generous back deck which overlooks a large back yard that backs up to trees. The storage building conveys. Schedule your tour today!
